Template::Plugin::HTML::2Text version 0.01
========================================

Template::Plugin::HTML::2Text - Template Toolkit plugin to transfer HTML into plain text

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   Template 
   HTML::FormatText::Html2text 

